1^2 + 2^2 + 3^2 + \cdots + (n-1)^2 \equiv 0 \, \text{mod n} \ \text{if and only if } n \equiv \pm 1 \, \text{mod} 6.
1^2 + 2^2 + 3^2 + \cdots + (n-1)^2 = \frac{(n-1)n(2n-1)}{6}.
6 \mid n-1 \Rightarrow n \equiv 1 \, \text{mod} 6
6 \mid n+1 \Rightarrow n \equiv -1 \, \text{mod} 6
1^2 + 2^2 + 3^2 + \ldots + (n-1)^2 + n^2 = \frac{n(n+1)(2n+1)}{6}.
